description:
Here's a preview of our all-new Patreon exclusive episode that finds the Losers gazing at the gargoyles within Stephen King's 1988 coffee table book Nightmares in the Sky. Want more? Head on over to www.patreon.com/thebarrens and become a Patron for more exclusive bonus content.
